'''Aeglos''' was a tall, thorny plant, similar to a gorse, but somewhat larger than that. Its sweet-smelling flowers were white, and from them it took its name: ''aeglos'' is [[Sindarin]] for "snow-thorn".<ref>{{UT|Narn}}, note 14</ref> It was found on the lower slopes of [[Amon Rûdh]],<ref>{{UT|Narn}} ''Of Mîm the Dwarf''</ref> upon the surrounding moors,<ref>{{CH|7}}, p. 128</ref> in West [[Beleriand]] and perhaps elsewhere. 
